Review_title: Tom Daley: Illegal to Be Me
Review_Text: A very interesting and thought provoking documentary actually, with Tom Daley proving to be a rather engaging and thoughtful presenter.I hope this goes some way to spark a sense of change.Good stuff.

It is shocking that this is still happening to homosexual people in 2022 :( :( :( :(
Hope this documentary will impact people to realize what is happening in the world.
